      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione pagina corpo numero : w-cnt-cor-nrp-dav   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-cor-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate, escluse fincature        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      10                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      17                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-cor-reg-150.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
