       vis-lin-cor-640.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Data scadenza                       *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-dts-sdb (1)    =    zero
                     go to vis-lin-cor-642
           else      go to vis-lin-cor-644.
       vis-lin-cor-642.
           move      " A vista"           to   w-lin-w02-dat-sca      .
           go to     vis-lin-cor-650.
       vis-lin-cor-644.
           move      "ED"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "D"                  to   v-tip                  .
