      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-axs-loc    =    spaces
                     go to pre-are-wcc-400.
       pre-are-wcc-320.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
