      *                          * documento                           *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-rig-tip-ddr (1)    =    01
                     go to pre-are-wcc-550
           else if   w-rig-tip-ddr (1)    =    02
                     go to pre-are-wcc-560
           else      go to pre-are-wcc-570.
       pre-are-wcc-550.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
