      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-sta-dis-wcc-iuv      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Area editata per la voce da stampare        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-sta-dis-wcc-edt      .
       pre-are-wcc-999.
